{"tid":2047443,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"TWICE 新歌橫掃海內外音源榜　達成「13 連勝」！","createTime":"2020-06-02T06:07:35.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-02T07:50:12.000Z","uid":16659,"like":2,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"e8b4e6b89ba6ece84880f0d6fb8bd439b3626e1b","tid":2047443,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:07:35.000Z","msg":"TWICE 自從出道以來，每次回歸都成功登上音源榜首，這次的最新作品〈MORE &amp; MORE〉當然也不例外！<br />\n<br />\n昨晚（1 日）發行第九張迷你專輯〈MORE &amp; MORE〉後不久，TWICE 的同名主打歌便已經登上 Genie、Bugs、MelOn 以及 Soribada 的即時榜寶座。今天上午除了這四個榜單外，在 NAVER 的「迅速上升榜」也成功奪冠。<br />\n<br />\n而在日本也享有高人氣的 TWICE，發片後不久同樣拿下 LINE Music 即時百大歌曲榜冠軍，收錄在〈MORE &amp; MORE〉中的 &ldquo;Firework&rdquo;、&rdquo;Make Me Go、&rdquo;Sweet Summer Day&rdquo;⋯⋯等歌亦列隊佔領前十名。<br />\n<br />\n不僅如此，〈MORE &amp; MORE〉也在日本、巴西、印尼、俄羅斯⋯⋯等 30 幾個國家的 iTunes 專輯榜上奪冠，成功為 TWICE 寫下出道以來的最佳成績，不愧是 TWICE 啊！<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n（照片或影片來源：JYP Entertainment）"},{"pid":"c418a3427ddb06d9d5578707ddf666afe9e86860","tid":2047443,"uid":20908,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:08:11.000Z","msg":"麻麻地<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b15d27f00304c160608f366164cbee83df88c37","tid":2047443,"uid":16659,"like":0,"dislike":7,"score":-7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-02T06:08:25.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/3ef4e7c84145878326c05c0295eca5c6/596ef3c76bace130-10/s1280x1920/cd0469840a5e5487ef819ba462c7c3dd3a533047.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F3ef4e7c84145878326c05c0295eca5c6%2F596ef3c76bace130-10%2Fs1280x1920%2Fcd0469840a5e5487ef819ba462c7c3dd3a533047.gifv&h=af37c6ff&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://66.media.tumblr.com/278fde64c7e3fa72f683f92815d4b2c8/596ef3c76bace130-aa/s1280x1920/e02829c92a418d44a6558fa140804ee0e0b49fa0.gifv\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2F66.media.tumblr.com%2F278fde64c7e3fa72f683f92815d4b2c8%2F596ef3c76bace130-aa%2Fs12